<h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 22px; color: #111827;">Reset Your Password</h2>

<p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">
    Hi{{#if userName}} <strong>{{userName}}</strong>{{/if}},
</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">
    We received a request to reset the password for your Zenith account. Click the button below to set a new password:
</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
    {{> button url=resetLink label="Reset Password"}}
</div>

<p style="margin: 24px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">
    Or copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
    <a href="{{{resetLink}}}" style="color: #2563eb; word-break: break-all;">{{resetLinkDisplay}}</a>
</p>

<p style="margin: 16px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af;">
    This link expires in <strong>{{expiresIn}}</strong>. If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore
    this email — your password will remain unchanged.
</p>